title: 1st Dinosaur eggs Avatar vote Part 1
body:
About Voting
To make it easier for you to vote, we have numbered each group of dinosaur Avatars. We will take a snapshot of all vDSG addresses at 8:00 (GMT) on October 19th, and airdrop a voting token based on the amount of vDSG. If you transfer the voting token, you will also lose the right to vote for this event.
Then, we will take a snapshot of the addresses with voting tokens at 8:30(GMT) on October 19th, and take the amount of voting tokens in the addresses at the time as voting rights.

There is one thing you need to pay attention to: you can choose to vote for multiple works, but your votes will be equally divided among all the works you choose. For example, if you have 100 votes and you choose to vote for 5 works, each of these 5 works will get 20 votes.
The deadline for voting is 8:00 on October 21, 2021 (GMT). At that time, we will select 20 lucky voters, each of whom will be awarded 50DSG.

Since there were so many artists' submissions and the snapshot choice options are limited, the vote will be divided into two parts, this is the first part.
